import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { LoginservisService } from '../servisi/loginservis.service'; import { Nastavnik } from '../models/nastavnik'; @Component({ selector: 'app-registernastavnik', templateUrl: './registernastavnik.component.html', styleUrls: ['./registernastavnik.component.css'] }) export class RegisternastavnikComponent { constructor(private servis: LoginservisService) {} selectedAges: string[] = []; user: Nastavnik = new Nastavnik() firststep : number = 0 goToSecondStep(){ const passwordRegex = /^(?=.*[A-Z])(?=.*[a-z]{3,})(?=.*\d)(?=.*[@$!%*?&])[A-Za-z\d@$!%*?&]{6,10}$/; if (!passwordRegex.test(this.user.password)) { alert('Format sifre je los ispravi'); return; } this.firststep++; } }
